## Additional Use Grant
You may use the Licensed Work for any purpose, including production use, provided that:  
- You may not use the Licensed Work to provide a "Nodes as a Service" (NaaS) or "Validators as a Service" (VaaS) offering.  
- **Definition of NaaS**: A "Nodes as a Service" offering is a commercial service where the Licensed Work is used to host, manage, or provide access to blockchain nodes for third parties (other than your employees or contractors acting on your behalf) in exchange for a fee, subscription, or other compensation.  
- **Definition of VaaS**: A "Validators as a Service" offering is a commercial service where the Licensed Work is used to host, manage, or provide access to blockchain validators or staking functionality for third parties (other than your employees or contractors acting on your behalf) in exchange for a fee, subscription, or other compensation.

